{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"기본적인 폼 힌트","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/forms/Basic_form_hints","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><span class=\"seoSummary\">전통적인 HTML 폼 관련 요소를 사용하여 폼을 구현할 때 컨트롤에 레이블을 지정하고 레이블을 컨트롤과 명시적으로&nbsp;연결하는 것이 중요합니다.</span>&nbsp;스크린 리더 사용자가 페이지를 탐색할 때, 스크린 리더는 폼 컨트롤을 알려주지만, 레이블과 폼이&nbsp;직접적으로 연결되지 않으면&nbsp;스크린 리더는 어떤 레이블이 적절한지&nbsp;알 방법이 없습니다.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>아래의 예는 레이블이 있는 간단한 폼을 보여줍니다.&nbsp;각<a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a> 요소는 <code>id</code>를 가지고 있고, 각<a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/label\"><code>&lt;label&gt;</code></a> 요소는 자신과 연결된 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a>의 id를 나타내는&nbsp;&nbsp;<code>for</code> 속성을 가지고 있습니다.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>form</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>wine-1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>checkbox<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>riesling<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>label</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">for</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>wine-1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Berg Rottland Riesling<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>wine-2<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>checkbox<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>pinot-blanc<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>label</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">for</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>wine-2<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Pinot Blanc<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>wine-3<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>checkbox<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>pinot-grigio<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>label</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">for</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>wine-3<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Pinot Grigio<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>wine-4<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>checkbox<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>gewurztraminer<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>label</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">for</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>wine-4<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Gewürztraminer<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>form</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"labeling_with_aria","title":"ARIA로 라벨링 하기","isH3":false,"content":"<p>HTML <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/label\"><code>&lt;label&gt;</code></a> 요소는 폼 관련 요소로 적당하지만, 많은 폼 컨트롤은 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div\"><code>&lt;div&gt;</code></a>나 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code></a>를 사용한 동적인 Javascript 위젯으로 구현되어있습니다.&nbsp;W3C의&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.w3.org/WAI/\" title=\"http://www.w3.org/WAI/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Accessibility Initiative</a>에서 만들어진&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.w3.org/WAI/standards-guidelines/aria/\" title=\"http://www.w3.org/WAI/intro/aria.php\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">WAI-ARIA</a>,&nbsp;<strong>Accessible Rich Internet Applications</strong>&nbsp;사양은 이러한 경우를 위해&nbsp;<code><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/2010/WD-wai-aria-20100916/states_and_properties#aria-labelledby\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">aria-labelledby</a></code>&nbsp;속성을 제공하고 있습니다.</p>\n\n<p>아래의 예에서는 순서 없는 리스트를 사용하여&nbsp;구현한&nbsp;라디오 버튼 그룹을 보여주고 있습니다. 3행의&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a> 요소에&nbsp;<code>aria-labelledby</code>&nbsp;속성에 라디오 그룹의 레이블인&nbsp;<a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h3&gt;</code></a> 요소의&nbsp;&nbsp;<code>id</code>&nbsp;&nbsp;<code>rg1_label</code>을 설정했습니다.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h3</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>rg1_label<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Lunch Options<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ul</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>radiogroup<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>rg1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>  <span class=\"token attr-name\">role</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>radiogroup<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-labelledby</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>rg1_label<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>r1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>  <span class=\"token attr-name\">tabindex</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>-1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">role</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>radio<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-checked</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>false<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">role</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>presentation<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>radio-unchecked.gif<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span> Thai\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>r2<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>  <span class=\"token attr-name\">tabindex</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>-1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">role</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>radio<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>  <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-checked</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>false<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">role</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>presentation<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>radio-unchecked.gif<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span> Subway\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>r3<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>   <span class=\"token attr-name\">tabindex</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">role</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>radio<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-checked</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>true<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">role</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>presentation<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>radio-checked.gif<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span> Radio Maria\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"describing_with_aria","title":"ARIA로 설명하기","isH3":false,"content":"<p>폼 컨트롤을 가끔 label 외에 추가설명이 있는 경우가 있다.&nbsp;ARIA는 <code><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/2010/WD-wai-aria-20100916/states_and_properties#aria-describedby\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">aria-describedby</a></code>&nbsp;속성을 사용하여 설명을 컨트롤과 직접 연관시킵니다.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>아래 예제는&nbsp;<a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div\"><code>&lt;div&gt;</code></a> 안의 문장이&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code></a> 요소를 설명하는 것을 보여줍니다. <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code></a>의&nbsp;&nbsp;<code>aria-describedby</code>&nbsp;속성은 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div\"><code>&lt;div&gt;</code></a>의 <code>id</code>를 참조합니다.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-describedby</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>descriptionRevert<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Revert<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>descriptionRevert<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Reverting will undo any changes that have been made\n                            since the last save.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong>Note</strong>: <code>aria-describedby</code>&nbsp;속성은 폼 컨트롤 외에도 다른 용도로 사용됩니다.&nbsp;</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"required_and_invalid_fields","title":"필수 필드와 유효하지 않은 필드&nbsp;","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>Note</strong>: 현재는&nbsp;전 세계 사용자의 97%가&nbsp;&nbsp;<code>required</code>를 사용할 수 있으므로&nbsp;<code>required</code>와&nbsp;<code>aria-required</code> 모두를 사용하는 것은 더는 권장하지 않습니다.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>일반적으로 웹 개발자는 필수 필드와 유효하지 않은 필드를 나타내기 위해서 시각적인 방법을 사용합니다. 보조 기술(ATs)은 언제나 표시된 것을 통해서&nbsp;정보를 추측하지는 않습니다.&nbsp;ARIA 는 폼 컨트롤의&nbsp;필수나 유효하지 않음을 나타내는 속성을 제공합니다.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>AT에 폼을 완료하기 위한 필수요소임을 알리기 위해<strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/2010/WD-wai-aria-20100916/states_and_properties#aria-required\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">aria-required</a></strong>&nbsp;속성을 폼에 적용할 수 있습니다.&nbsp;</li>\n <li>데이터 필드에 올바르지 않은 데이터가 있는 것을 AT에 알리기 위해<strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/2010/WD-wai-aria-20100916/states_and_properties#aria-invalid\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">aria-invalid</a></strong>&nbsp;상태를 적용하는 것으로 사용자는 올바르지 않은 데이터를 입력했다는 것을 알 수 있습니다.&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>아래의 예제는 세 개의 필드가 있는 간단한 폼을 보여줍니다. 4행과 12행에서는 <code>aria-required</code>&nbsp;속성이 true(레이블 옆에 별표와 함께)로 설정되어 name과 email 필드가 필수임을 나타냅니다.&nbsp;두 번째 예제는 email 형식을 검증하고 그 결과에 따라서 email 필드(HTML 12행)의 (요소를 시각적으로 변경하는 것과 함께) <code>aria-invalid</code>&nbsp;속성을 설정하는 Javascript 스니펫입니다.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>form</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>label</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">for</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>* Name:<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-required</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>true<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>label</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">for</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>phone<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Phone:<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>phone<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>phone<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-required</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>false<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>label</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">for</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>email<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>* E-mail:<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>email<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>email<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-required</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>true<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>form</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>폼 항목의 유효성을 검사하는 스크립트는 다음과 같습니다.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">validate</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> emailElement <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>emailFieldId<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> valid <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">emailValid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>formData<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>email<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// returns true if valid, false otherwise</span>\n\n  emailElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setAttribute</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"aria-invalid\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!</span>valid<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">setElementBorderColour</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>emailElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> valid<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// sets the border to red if second arg is false</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"필수 필드와 유효하지 않은 필드 "}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"providing_helpful_error_messages","title":"유용한 오류 메시지 제공","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/forms/alerts\" title=\"aria/forms/alerts\">ARIA alerts to enhance forms</a>&nbsp;사용법을 읽으세요.</p>\n\n<p>폼&nbsp;접근성을위한 ARIA 사용에 대한 자세한 지침은&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/wai-aria-practices/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">WAI-ARIA Authoring Practices</a>&nbsp;문서를 참조하세요.&nbsp;</p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"ARIA로 라벨링 하기","id":"labeling_with_aria"},{"text":"ARIA로 설명하기","id":"describing_with_aria"},{"text":"필수 필드와 유효하지 않은 필드&nbsp;","id":"required_and_invalid_fields"},{"text":"유용한 오류 메시지 제공","id":"providing_helpful_error_messages"}],"summary":"전통적인 HTML 폼 관련 요소를 사용하여 폼을 구현할 때 컨트롤에 레이블을 지정하고 레이블을 컨트롤과 명시적으로 연결하는 것이 중요합니다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Basic form hints","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Consejos básicos para formularios","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Indications élémentaires pour les formulaires","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"基本的なフォームのヒント","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Dicas básicas de form","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"基本表單應用","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/accessibility/aria/forms/basic_form_hints","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/accessibility/aria/forms/basic_form_hints/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web","title":"개발자를 위한 웹 기술"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/Accessibility","title":"접근성"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA","title":"ARIA"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/forms","title":"Forms"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/forms/Basic_form_hints","title":"기본적인 폼 힌트"}],"pageTitle":"기본적인 폼 힌트 - 접근성 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}